SELECT [t].[WorkStationId], [t].[Pressure], [t].[ProductionLineId], [t].[StationName], [t].[Status], [t].[Temperature], [a].[AlarmId], [a].[MaxPressure], [a].[MaxTemperature], [a].[MinPressure], [a].[MinTemperature], [a].[WorkStationId]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [w].[WorkStationId], [w].[Pressure], [w].[ProductionLineId], [w].[StationName], [w].[Status], [w].[Temperature]
    FROM [WorkStations] AS [w]
    WHERE ((([w].[Pressure] >= @__entity_MinPressure_0) AND ([w].[Pressure] <= @__entity_MaxPressure_1)) AND ([w].[Temperature] >= @__entity_MinTemperature_2)) AND ([w].[Temperature] <= @__entity_MaxTemperature_3)
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Alarms] AS [a] ON [t].[WorkStationId] = [a].[WorkStationId]
ORDER BY [t].[WorkStationId]

SELECT [a].[AlarmId], [a].[MaxPressure], [a].[MaxTemperature], [a].[MinPressure], [a].[MinTemperature], [a].[WorkStationId], [w].[WorkStationId], [w].[Pressure], [w].[ProductionLineId], [w].[StationName], [w].[Status], [w].[Temperature], [t].[MaintenancePersonnelsMaintenancePersonnelId], [t].[WorkStationsWorkStationId], [t].[MaintenancePersonnelId], [t].[EmailAdress], [t].[Name], [t].[PhoneNumber], [t].[Surname]
FROM [Alarms] AS [a]
LEFT JOIN [WorkStations] AS [w] ON [a].[WorkStationId] = [w].[WorkStationId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [m].[MaintenancePersonnelsMaintenancePersonnelId], [m].[WorkStationsWorkStationId], [m0].[MaintenancePersonnelId], [m0].[EmailAdress], [m0].[Name], [m0].[PhoneNumber], [m0].[Surname]
    FROM [MaintenancePersonnelWorkStation] AS [m]
    INNER JOIN [MaintenancePersonnels] AS [m0] ON [m].[MaintenancePersonnelsMaintenancePersonnelId] = [m0].[MaintenancePersonnelId]
) AS [t] ON [w].[WorkStationId] = [t].[WorkStationsWorkStationId]
ORDER BY [a].[AlarmId], [w].[WorkStationId], [t].[MaintenancePersonnelsMaintenancePersonnelId], [t].[WorkStationsWorkStationId]

SELECT [a].[AlarmId], [a].[MaxPressure], [a].[MaxTemperature], [a].[MinPressure], [a].[MinTemperature], [a].[WorkStationId], [w].[WorkStationId], [w].[Pressure], [w].[ProductionLineId], [w].[StationName], [w].[Status], [w].[Temperature], [t].[MaintenancePersonnelsMaintenancePersonnelId], [t].[WorkStationsWorkStationId], [t].[MaintenancePersonnelId], [t].[EmailAdress], [t].[Name], [t].[PhoneNumber], [t].[Surname]
FROM [Alarms] AS [a]
LEFT JOIN [WorkStations] AS [w] ON [a].[WorkStationId] = [w].[WorkStationId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [m].[MaintenancePersonnelsMaintenancePersonnelId], [m].[WorkStationsWorkStationId], [m0].[MaintenancePersonnelId], [m0].[EmailAdress], [m0].[Name], [m0].[PhoneNumber], [m0].[Surname]
    FROM [MaintenancePersonnelWorkStation] AS [m]
    INNER JOIN [MaintenancePersonnels] AS [m0] ON [m].[MaintenancePersonnelsMaintenancePersonnelId] = [m0].[MaintenancePersonnelId]
) AS [t] ON [w].[WorkStationId] = [t].[WorkStationsWorkStationId]
ORDER BY [a].[AlarmId], [w].[WorkStationId], [t].[MaintenancePersonnelsMaintenancePersonnelId], [t].[WorkStationsWorkStationId]
